Source: pg-slug-gen
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/fernandoolle/pg_slug_gen

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pg-slug-gen
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pg-slug-gen
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Generate cryptographically secure timestamp-based slugs
  pg_slug_gen generates unique random slugs based on timestamps with
  cryptographically secure character selection for PostgreSQL 15 through 18.
